Judul: Abundant rare isotopes  in a planetary nebula
Abstrak:
The origin of the chemical elements in the Universe is one of the most fascinating 
and enduring mysteries in astronomy. Progress so far has come from studies of stars, 
but here only elemental abundances can be determined reliably. Isotopic ratios are more 
difficult to obtain.
Fakultas: Fakultas Matematika dan Ilmu Pengetahuan Alam
